title: Neenah Astrodesigns/Creative Collection Starter Kit Cardstock, 4.5" x 6.5", 65 lb/176 GSM, 18-Color Assortment, 72 Sheets (46416-03)
description: Out with the old, in with the new! The Creative Collection 18-Color Starter Pack you once knew is receiving a brand upgrade and new colors! The new Astrodesigns 18-Color Assortment features 8 brand new colors and with 72 sheets per pack, will still offer the bright, bold colors it always has. Each 4.5" x 6.5" sheet features a vibrant color for everyday and special occasion projects. Astrodesigns paper is compatible with copiers, inkjet, and laser printers for striking and impressive prints. Plus, it’s lignin and acid-free so your creations won’t yellow over time. New colors, same great quality paper!
